{
  "code": "3.5.4",
  "module": "3",
  "moduleTitle": "Disclosure of risks and opportunities",
  "questionText": "What is your strategy for complying with the systems you are regulated by or anticipate being regulated by?",
  "questionKo": "규제를 받고 있거나 규제 적용 예정인 탄소가격시스템에 대한 귀사의 대응 전략을 입력하십시오 .",
  "questionType": "RICH_TEXT",
  "mandatory": "False",
  "issueTags": "Climate Change",
  "sectorTags": "Oil & Gas, Coal, General, Aviation, Capital goods, Transport OEMS - EPM, Chemicals, Metals & mining, Transport services, Steel, Agricultural commodities, Transport OEMS, Energy utilities & power generators, Cement, Food, beverage & tobacco, Paper & forestry, Real estate, Construction",
  "simpleHelp": "This question provides data users with insight into an organization's long-term compliance and regulatory risk management strategy for the carbon pricing systems they are regulated by or anticipate being regulated by.",
  "popupHelp": "",
  "baseOptions": [],
  "rows": [],
